\pard\plain \li720\sb180\qj\ltrch\loch {\f1\fs24\b1\i0 Thought 3}{\f0\fs24\b0\i0 . Romans 4:11 says that God gave circumcision to Abraham for two reasons: to be a sign of Abraham\loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8217\'92s faith and to be the seal of Abraham\u8217\'92s righteousness. Note the verse:\{\\Scrv_fn=}{\f3\fs24\b0\i0  Leadership Ministries Worldwide. (1996). \\end_Scrv_fn\}\{\\Scrv_fn=}{\field{\*\fldinst HYPERLINK "https://ref.ly/logosres/posbkjv01ge2?ref=Bible.Ge17.9-14&off=5362&ctx=e+flesh%E2%80%9D+(Ph.+3:3).%0a~Thought+2.+Old+Testa"}{\fldrslt\f4\fs24\b0\i1\ul\ulc0\cf3 Genesis (Chapters 12\endash 50)\\end_Scrv_fn\}\{\\Scrv_fn=}}{\f3\fs24\b0\i0  (Vol. II, p. 84). Chattanooga, TN: Leadership Ministries Worldwide.\\end_Scrv_fn\}}
